      <title>Istio 和 Kubernetes 帮助 Trulia 房产网站消除单体架构增强微服务的可观测性</title>
      <link>https://cloudnativecn.com/blog/microservice-observability-with-istio/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Sep 2018 15:49:30 +0800</pubDate>
